<li><i>The Odyssey: A Modern Sequel</i>, translation in verses by Kimon Friar, New York: Simon and Schuster, 1958; London: <a href="/wiki/Secker_and_Warburg" title="Secker and Warburg">Secker and Warburg</a>, 1958.</li>
<li><i>Death, the Ant</i>, from <i>The Odyssey: A Modern Sequel</i>, Book XV, 829-63, translated by Kimon Friar, "<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Charioteer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Charioteer (page does not exist)">The Charioteer</a>", No. 1 (Summer 1960), p. 39.</li>
