<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Last_Temptation_of_Christ" title="The Last Temptation of Christ">The Last Temptation</a></i>, translated by Peter A. Bien, New York, Simon and Schuster, 1960; New York, Bantam Books, 1961; Oxford: Bruno Cassirer, 1961; London: Faber and Faber, 1975.</li>
<li><i>Saint Francis</i>, translated by Peter A. Bien, New York: Simon and Schuster, 1962; published in the United Kingdom as <i>God's Pauper: Saint Francis of Assisi</i>, Oxford: Bruno Cassirer, 1962, 1975; London: Faber and Faber, 1975.</li>
<li><i>The Fratricides</i>, translated by Athena Gianakas Dallas, New York: Simon &amp; Schuster, 1964</li>
