<li><i>The Homeric G.B.S.</i>, "<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Shaw_Review&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Shaw Review (page does not exist)">The Shaw Review</a>" 18, No. 3 (Sept. 1975), pp. 91-92. Greek original written for a 1946 Greek language radio broadcast by BBC Overseas Service, on the occasion of <a href="/wiki/George_Bernard_Shaw" title="George Bernard Shaw">George Bernard Shaw</a>'s 90th birthday.</li>
